creator: CoachElite
descriptionHtml:
If you are downloading this app, you are a client of a coach who has chosen to level up and subscribe to what is soon to be the best coaching app on the market.

CoachElite allows athletes to easily view and log all of the workouts assigned to them by their coach. Athletes can also give detailed feedback on each and every exercise, right down to their achieved sets, reps, weight and RPE.

No more back-and-forth emails, spreadsheets, and text messages and start getting real results with CoachElite today.
descriptionShort: The easiest app for giving your coach detailed feedback on your workouts.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: This is the launch of our Beta version on the app store.
